Title: [ANN][ICO] ‚öΩRANKINGBALL‚öæ Sports/Esports Daily Fantasy Bingo!
Body: Great question Liberoops.  RankingBall is not a gambling site. It is a strategic skill game where users play against each other, not the house. Essentially it's a Peer-to-Peer game.  Those who play on RankingBall are all subject to the same rules and scoring system, which is posted on our site, which creates a level playing field. We base our scoring system off of real sport or esport game stats, which can not be manipulated. Also, those who work at or are affiliated with RankingBall are never allowed to play on the site, gameplay is only open to the fans.  Our token makes it so that every transaction and contest is transparent and recorded on the blockchain. So it's all out there for everyone to see where the tokens are going.  One of the goals of RankingBall is to bring the power back to the sports and esports community. We want a have fun and safe environment for all of those who play.

Author: Conrad010
Title: [ANN][ICO] ‚öΩRANKINGBALL‚öæ Sports/Esports Daily Fantasy Bingo!
Body: Users will pay to take part in contests on the RankingBall platform. The type of contest will dictate how they will pay for entry. These contests are RankingBall Silver, RankingBall Gold and Fiat currency contests. Here is an overview of how they work:  ‚ñ™ RankingBall Silver Contest: RankingBall Silver (RBS) is a Universal Game Money within RankingBall, and a small amount is given to all players upon signing up. RBS is used to join contests and is given out as rewards after the contest. Top ranked players are awarded bonus RankingBall Gold. Players can purchase additional RBS on Android or IOS Market via in-app purchases.  ‚ñ™ RankingBall Gold Contest: RankingBall Gold (RBG) is a Universal Game Money that can be purchased as ETH or other coin (TBD) on exchanges linked to the players‚Äô electronic wallet and API. Rewards for this contest are paid out in RBG.  ‚ñ™ Fiat Money Contest: Where allowed, contestants can use regulated fiat currency to join contests and also earn rewards in fiat currency.

Author: zoLa#7
Title: [ANN][ICO] ‚öΩRANKINGBALL‚öæ Sports/Esports Daily Fantasy Bingo!
Body: Two loyalty programs exist within the RankingBall service. RBG earned through loyalty programs can only be used within RankingBall (as entry fees for RBG contests) and cannot be exchanged on external exchanges to fiat money.   1. Internal Loyalty Program  Players can participate in RBS contests to earn RBS and RBG as bonuses. RBG token holders can participate in special sports/esports events (World Cup, Olympics, final matches, etc.) or Special Promotion GPP (Guaranteed Pool Prize) Contests to earn additional RBG on top of basic rewards.  2. External Loyalty Program  RBG is awarded to users who meet certain criteria on external platforms (e.g. viewers on Steam, Twitch, and Sports Media who play/watch for a certain number of hours) in partnership with game publishers and sports media. This in turn attracts those viewers to RankingBall Platform to join contests.  Read more about RankingBall project on https://www.scribd.com/document/372502435/Ranking-Ball-Gold-White-Paper.  Follow RankingBall on Twitter, https://twitter.com/RankingBall.  Join official RankingBall Telegram community on https://t.me/RankingBallPublic.

The second type of contest is the RankingBall Gold (RBG) contest: RBG can be purchased as ETH or other coins (TBD) on exchanges linked to the players‚Äô electronic wallet and API. RBG can be used to join RBG contests, the rewards of which are given as RBG.  There is also the Fiat Money contest: In jurisdictions where this type of contest is allowed, (including 30 states in the US, Europe and some Asian countries) players sign up with fiat money to play for a chance to earn fiat rewards.  This variety of contests allows everyone to get involved in this exciting, play-by play strategy game.

Author: RBGold
Title: [ANN][ICO] ‚öΩRANKINGBALL‚öæ Sports/Esports Daily Fantasy Bingo!
Body: Transforming fans of sports and esports from idle spectators to fully engaged participants!   Bounty | Website | White Paper | Facebook | Twitter | Medium | Reddit  Follow the action - Join our Telegram Channel!  Token Sale starts June 11th. Register Now!  RANKINGBALL SITE IS NOW LIVE. COME PLAY THE FANTASY SPORTS BINGO!  <<<RANKINGBALL PLAY SITE>>>  BOUNTY NOW LIVE  <<<OFFICIAL BOUNTY THREAD>>>  The Bounty program will run until the end of the token sale, July 2nd  Find about more HERE        RankingBall is an innovative gaming platform that unlocks a new future for sports and esports, transforming fans from idle spectators to fully engaged participants. RankingBall has developed its own skill-based game using real-time data from live sports and esports events to merge Daily Fantasy Sports (DFS) with Bingo. This gameplay allows fans to put their skills to the test while also leveling the playing field on the blockchain.  The RankingBall platform allows users to participate in DFS Bingo contests while watching real live matches, have fun by competing with other players, and to earn rewards based on their performance. RankingBall‚Äôs ecosystem is also rewarding by allowing users to earn RankingBall Gold (blockchain token) by playing their favorite online video games, or even use RBG to support their favorite streamers, pros, and developers. With these features, RankingBall is ready to create a unique gaming platform and lead the world of sports and esports entertainment.          Real-time Data  Our first unbeatable advantage over competitors is data. Real-time sports and esports data comes in many different forms and from many different providers. We‚Äôve spent years working to ensure that we can reliably integrate real-time data feeds into RankingBall, making play-by-play skill-based sports betting possible for the first time.  Minimum Media Latency  We also spent significant time tuning our platform so that it is synced with the 20-40 second broadcast delay, which varies by broadcaster. We spent two grueling years attending sporting events to develop and test solutions to the latency issue.  Bingo Game Logic  Another unbeatable advantage we are implementing is the way players engage with the sports they are watching all within one app. By combining all of the best elements from existing fantasy sports websites and adding our unique bingo like card format we can add more excitement and competitiveness to the way sports are viewed.  Global Partnerships  In our home market, Korea, we already have partnerships and have run tests with three major sports networks. Globally, we are in talks with ESPN, CBS, NBC and FOX, who like how RankingBall encourages more engagement with live broadcasts. In the world of esports, we‚Äôre already working closely with Player Unknown‚Äôs Battleground, which will kick off this year. We‚Äôre also working to offer other popular titles like LOL, DOTA2 and CS:GO.             RankingBall‚Äôs blockchain platform will act as a bridge connecting gamers, sports and esports media, game developers and publishers, so they can create and share new value. We will issue our own blockchain-based currency, RankingBall Gold (RBG), which improves convenience for players and makes games more fun, while also increasing the efficiency and security for our platform.  RBG is a decentralized ERC20 token on the Ethereum blockchain. It enables us to develop a new and innovative cryptocurrency ecosystem within the platform, using smart contract technology.  Token Objective  RankingBall has developed an innovative gaming platform which will disrupt the traditional sports and e-sports gaming industries. This comes at an ideal time, coinciding with the emergence of blockchain technology and the crypto economy, which are acting as disruptors across a wide swath of industries. Until now, gaming companies have spent enormous time and money to comply with local rules, regulations and licensing requirements related to gaming, payments, KYC and AML before they can launch their businesses.  By issuing our Ethereum-based RankingBall Gold (RBG) token, we solve many of the issues related to regulations across multiple regions. This allows us to create a new player contest system with an entry fee and reward structure. In addition to the in-platform token economy, RankingBall offers a loyalty program in partnership with external platforms with token economy. We believe this will allow RankingBall to not only lead the sports/esports gaming frontier, but also create a whole new ecosystem that connects gamers, sports/esports media, and game developer/publisher.
